data.description: Charmer home in quiet neighborhood in Englewood! Cozy family room with woodburning fireplace with hardwood floors.  Kitchen has VPF with large extra room for dinning with bar.  Walk into Laundry room from garage.  Master bedroom has double closets and attached 1/2 bath. Backyard is fenced in.  FP/Chimney not warranted.
